        <text><![CDATA[ <p> <strong>Rural Opportunity Zone and Investment Act </strong></p> <p>This bill provides for the deferral of tax until December 31, 2032, on capital gains invested in qualified rural opportunity zones. A q<em>ualified rural opportunity zone</em> is any population census tract that is located in a rural county and is in persistent poverty.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
